<Author>hanwellhavoc
<Content>Excellent Hotel! Stayed 3 nights at the NH Sant Angelo, and what a wonderful stay it was!Check in was very efficient and polite, and very helpful.Our room was large(unlike some other reviewers?), spotless and tidied daily.The breakfast buffet is great...fresh fruit, cereals, pastries, a few hot options, toast, juices, tea, coffee, yoghurt, etc.Free soap, shower gel, shampoo, conditioner, comb, razor and foam, toothbrush and paste, chocolates and mints. Lovely soft fluffy towels. Large TV. Fridge(mini bar). It is a few minutes walk from a couple of Metro stations and the bus stop is around the corner.It is in a lovely part of the city..near to everything but without the noise of being too close to Las Ramblas.All in all, we had a brilliant stay, and would definetly stay here again.Thanks!!!! 
