<Content>Lovely hotel NH Sant Angelo We have just returned from a weekend break in Barcelona with 2 friends. We booked through an online hotel site. The hotel is in the city centre next to Joan Miro park and we paid 拢60 per night per room. My friends had been to other NH hotels, and this was just as nice  clean, decorated in a contemporary style. Breakfast was not included (like most of the hotels in Barcelona). It is located 5 minutes walk from Sants train/metro station  3 minutes walk from Espanya  Tarragona metro stations. We bought 3 day travelcards for 拢13 and thus travelled throughout the city. The nearby restaurants are authentic Catalan, but this means Spanish only menus.We definitely recommend staying here if going to Barcelona. 
