<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Easy to get to, Clean and efficient Stayed at this hotel for a long Weekend while in Barcelona on holiday.Was the cheapest I could find which belonged to a reliable chain, although I had never used NH before. Hotel was absolutely spotless, in a good location- about 5 minutes walk from the Metro station where trains run till 2am Fri/Sat and midnight the rest of the week. Room was small but well furnished and comfortable, it looked out on an internal 'space' but for the price we paid was good. A/C was a bit dodge but couldn't be bothered asking for another room and moving stuff, opened window instead. Not all staff spoke English and this hotel certainly showed it was a Spanish chain, however I speak minimal Spanish and got by. Certainly would stay again. 
